Note on engine licensing: this repository (chordTUI's own code) is MIT. The
default-installed analysis engine (librosa, ISC) is license-clean. Optional,
user-opted-in engines carry their own terms — madmom's pretrained models are
CC-BY-NC-SA 4.0 (NonCommercial) and essentia is AGPL-3.0. They are never
installed by default. See README / docs for details.
